label: ABC_tP6_129_c_c_c-001
title: CaGaN Structure
comments:
There are two prototypes with the AFLOW label ABC\_tP6\_129\_c\_c\_c: \begin{itemize} \item \href{current_web_home_dir/ABC_tP6_129_c_c_c-001}{CaGaN} (this structure), with c/a $\approx$ 2.1, and \item \href{current_web_home_dir/ABC_tP6_129_c_c_c-002}{TaMoN}, with c/a $\approx$ 2.5. \end{itemize} ~ \vspace{-0.25in} 
 (Verdier, 1974) give the atomic coordinates in setting 1 of space group $P4/nmm$ \#129.  We shifted the origin to place the system in our standard setting 2.
